        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "There’s a lot of unpleasant news out there right now, so I thought I would share some fun news for a change: I’m co-producing the upcoming Adam McKay blockbuster film called ",
