        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "I’ve been working with Adam and journalist Ron Suskind on the project for a while, and the news of the film is now public. This new role is in addition to my ongoing reporting here at ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
